  "remarks": "Igor Kudryashkin is a Russian businessperson with extensive business interests in the Russian mining and metals sectors. In particular, Kudryashkin is a shareholder and Commercial Director of Ural Mining and Metallurgical Company, a major Russian company engaged in the Russian mining and metals sectors. Those economic sectors provide a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation.",
